{"remainingRequest":"/Users/zhoubichuan/Desktop/web/Web-Nginx/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js??ref--1-1!/Users/zhoubichuan/Desktop/web/Web-Nginx/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js??ref--1-2!/Users/zhoubichuan/Desktop/web/Web-Nginx/src/base/practice/1.Nginx.md?vue&type=template&id=02609f7f&","dependencies":[{"path":"/Users/zhoubichuan/Desktop/web/Web-Nginx/src/base/practice/1.Nginx.md","mtime":1625067735369},{"path":"/Users/zhoubichuan/Desktop/web/Web-Nginx/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/zhoubichuan/Desktop/web/Web-Nginx/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/loaders/templateLoader.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/zhoubichuan/Desktop/web/Web-Nginx/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/zhoubichuan/Desktop/web/Web-Nginx/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/zhoubichuan/Desktop/web/Web-Nginx/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js","mtime":499162500000}],"contextDependencies":[],"result":["\n<div class=\"content\"><h1 id=\"安装-nginx\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#安装-nginx\">#</a> 安装 Nginx</h1>\n<h2 id=\"_1-安装所需依赖\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_1-安装所需依赖\">#</a> 1. 安装所需依赖</h2>\n<p>在安装 Nginx 之前，需要安装 device-mapper-persistent-data 和 lvm2 两个依赖：\n我们使用使用 Yum 命令安装依赖：</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-text\"><code>yum install -y yum-utils device-mapper-persistent-data lvm2\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers-wrapper\"><span class=\"line-number\">1</span><br></div><!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><blockquote>\n<p>device-mapper-persistent-data: 存储驱动，Linux 上的许多高级卷管理技术,lvm: 逻辑卷管理器，用于创建逻辑磁盘分区使用</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"_2-使用阿里云源安装-nginx\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_2-使用阿里云源安装-nginx\">#</a> 2. 使用阿里云源安装 Nginx</h2>\n<p>接下来，添加阿里云的 Nginx 镜像源，加速 Nginx 的安装</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-text\"><code>sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo http://mirrors.aliyun.com/Nginx-ce/linux/centos/Nginx-ce.repo\nyum install Nginx-ce\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers-wrapper\"><span class=\"line-number\">1</span><br><span class=\"line-number\">2</span><br></div><!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><h2 id=\"_3-启动-nginx\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_3-启动-nginx\">#</a> 3. 启动 Nginx</h2>\n<p>使用 systemctl 启动 Nginx</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-text\"><code>systemctl start Nginx\nsystemctl enable Nginx\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers-wrapper\"><span class=\"line-number\">1</span><br><span class=\"line-number\">2</span><br></div><!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><h2 id=\"_4-验证安装成功\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_4-验证安装成功\">#</a> 4. 验证安装成功</h2>\n<p>执行 Nginx -v ，如果展示以下信息，代表安装成功。</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-text\"><code>Nginx -v\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers-wrapper\"><span class=\"line-number\">1</span><br></div><!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><h2 id=\"_5-配置阿里云源\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_5-配置阿里云源\">#</a> 5. 配置阿里云源</h2>\n<p>我们拉取 Nginx 镜像时，一般默认会去 Nginx 官方源拉取镜像。但是国内出海网速实在是太慢，所以我们更换为 阿里云镜像仓库 源进行镜像下载加速\n登录阿里云官网，打开 阿里云容器镜像服务。点击左侧菜单最下面的 镜像加速器 ，选择 Centos （如下图）\n按照官网的提示，执行命令，即可实现更换 Nginx 镜像源地址</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-text\"><code>mkdir /etc/Nginx\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers-wrapper\"><span class=\"line-number\">1</span><br></div><!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><p>然后创建并编写配置文件：</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-text\"><code>vim /etc/Nginx/daemon.json\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers-wrapper\"><span class=\"line-number\">1</span><br></div><!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><p>只需要将加速器地址对应的 json 部分复制进 daemon.json 文件即可。</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-text\"><code>{\n  &quot;registry-mirrors&quot;: [&quot;https://unbgcuqt.mirror.aliyuncs.com&quot;]\n}\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers-wrapper\"><span class=\"line-number\">1</span><br><span class=\"line-number\">2</span><br><span class=\"line-number\">3</span><br></div><!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--><p>最后重启 Nginx：</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-sh line-numbers-mode\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-text\"><code>sudo systemctl daemon-reload\nsudo systemctl restart Nginx\n</code></pre>\n<div class=\"line-numbers-wrapper\"><span class=\"line-number\">1</span><br><span class=\"line-number\">2</span><br></div><!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--></div>\n",null]}